Thanks to everyone for the responses, all shed some new light for me, but I have another weird question...

I've had two really good games as Soraka, one with S-, one with S+.......and I get censored on chat for saying "S+ Raka"? What's wrong with that? I know about like boasting about scores or whatnot but I kinda do feel proud of my Ss.....is Riot trying to stop people from boasting? 

